WEBVTT

1
00:01:48.609 --> 00:01:50.642
        (Bird cawing)

2
00:02:41.244 --> 00:02:44.329
     Nan: THE LITTLE LORD'S
     BEEN DREAMING AGAIN.

3
00:02:47.384 --> 00:02:48.516
          (Growling)

4
00:02:50.604 --> 00:02:54.272
  WE HAVE VISITORS.
  I DON'T WANT TO SEE ANYONE.

5
00:02:54.341 --> 00:02:57.292
      REALLY ? IF I WAS
      COOPED UP ALL DAY...

6
00:02:57.360 --> 00:03:00.128
  WITH NO ONE BUT THIS OLD BAT
  FOR COMPANY. I'D GO MAD.

7
00:03:01.731 --> 00:03:04.065
     ANYWAY. YOU DON'T HAVE
     A CHOICE. ROBB'S WAITING.

8
00:03:04.134 --> 00:03:07.118
             I DON'T WANT TO GO.
NEITHER DO I.

9
00:03:07.187 --> 00:03:09.054
BUT ROBB'S
LORD OF WINTERFELL...

10
00:03:09.122 --> 00:03:12.057
WHICH MEANS
I DO WHAT HE SAYS.
AND YOU DO WHAT I SAY.

11
00:03:13.076 --> 00:03:15.277
HODOR !

12
00:03:18.515 --> 00:03:21.500
           HODOR ?
HELP BRAN DOWN THE HALL.

13
00:03:21.569 --> 00:03:23.468
         Hodor: HODOR.

14
00:03:29.542 --> 00:03:33.278
  Tyrion: I MUST SAY.
  I RECEIVED A SLIGHTLY WARMER
  WELCOME ON MY LAST VISIT.

15
00:03:33.347 --> 00:03:36.097
  Robb:
  ANY MAN OF THE NIGHT'S WATCH
  IS WELCOME AT WINTERFELL.

16
00:03:36.166 --> 00:03:39.017
 ANY MAN OF THE NIGHT'S WATCH.
 BUT NOT I. EH. BOY ?

17
00:03:39.086 --> 00:03:41.019
       I'M NOT YOUR BOY.
       LANNISTER.

18
00:03:41.087 --> 00:03:43.154
    I'M LORD OF WINTERFELL
    WHILE MY FATHER IS AWAY.

19
00:03:43.223 --> 00:03:46.374
            THEN YOU MIGHT LEARN
            A LORD'S COURTESY.
         (Door opens)

20
00:03:49.646 --> 00:03:51.129
         SO IT'S TRUE.

21
00:03:52.366 --> 00:03:54.582
          HELLO. BRAN.

22
00:03:54.651 --> 00:03:56.968
    DO YOU REMEMBER ANYTHING
    ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED ?

23
00:03:57.037 --> 00:03:59.587
       HE HAS NO MEMORY
       OF THAT DAY.

24
00:03:59.656 --> 00:04:02.173
                        CURIOUS.
       WHY ARE YOU HERE ?

25
00:04:03.760 --> 00:04:06.711
 WOULD YOUR CHARMING COMPANION
 BE SO KIND AS TO KNEEL ?

26
00:04:06.780 --> 00:04:09.947
 MY NECK IS BEGINNING TO HURT.
         KNEEL. HODOR.

27
00:04:12.852 --> 00:04:16.288
DO YOU LIKE TO RIDE. BRAN ?
                            YES.

28
00:04:16.356 --> 00:04:17.855
                  WELL. I MEAN.
                  I DID LIKE TO.

29
00:04:17.924 --> 00:04:19.807
      THE BOY HAS LOST
      THE USE OF HIS LEGS.

30
00:04:19.876 --> 00:04:22.610
        WHAT OF IT ? WITH THE
        RIGHT HORSE AND SADDLE.
        EVEN A CRIPPLE CAN RIDE.

31
00:04:22.679 --> 00:04:25.630
     I'M NOT A CRIPPLE.
           THEN I'M NOT A DWARF.

32
00:04:25.699 --> 00:04:27.782
             MY FATHER WILL
             REJOICE TO HEAR IT.

33
00:04:27.851 --> 00:04:28.950
          I HAVE A GIFT FOR YOU.

34
00:04:30.420 --> 00:04:33.088
      GIVE THAT TO YOUR SADDLER.
      HE'LL PROVIDE THE REST.

35
00:04:34.808 --> 00:04:37.625
             YOU MUST SHAPE THE
             HORSE TO THE RIDER.

36
00:04:37.695 --> 00:04:39.961
         START WITH A YEARLING
         AND TEACH IT TO RESPOND
         TO THE REINS...

37
00:04:40.030 --> 00:04:41.163
                    AND TO THE
                    BOY'S VOICE.

38
00:04:42.632 --> 00:04:44.499
        WILL I REALLY BE
        ABLE TO RIDE ?

39
00:04:44.568 --> 00:04:46.184
           YOU WILL.

40
00:04:46.253 --> 00:04:48.553
    ON HORSEBACK YOU WILL BE
    AS TALL AS ANY OF THEM.

41
00:04:48.622 --> 00:04:51.857
 IS THIS SOME KIND OF TRICK ?
 WHY DO YOU WANT TO HELP HIM ?

42
00:04:51.925 --> 00:04:53.291
      I HAVE A TENDER SPOT
      IN MY HEART...

43
00:04:53.360 --> 00:04:56.043
     FOR CRIPPLES. BASTARDS
     AND BROKEN THINGS.

44
00:04:57.764 --> 00:04:59.664
     YOU'VE DONE MY BROTHER
     A KINDNESS.

45
00:04:59.733 --> 00:05:02.050
    THE HOSPITALITY
    OF WINTERFELL IS YOURS.

46
00:05:02.119 --> 00:05:05.620
SPARE ME YOUR FALSE COURTESIES.
LORD STARK.

47
00:05:05.689 --> 00:05:07.422
      THERE'S A BROTHEL
      OUTSIDE YOUR WALLS.

48
00:05:07.491 --> 00:05:11.076
     THERE I'LL FIND A BED
     AND BOTH OF US CAN
     SLEEP EASIER.

49
00:05:15.415 --> 00:05:17.999
      COULDN'T RESIST
      SOME NORTHERN ARSE ?

50
00:05:18.068 --> 00:05:20.468
           IF YOU LIKE REDHEADS.
           ASK FOR ROS.

51
00:05:20.537 --> 00:05:23.721
COME TO SEE ME OFF. GREYJOY ?
KIND OF YOU.

52
00:05:23.790 --> 00:05:25.874
YOUR MASTER DOESN'T SEEM
TO LIKE LANNISTERS.

53
00:05:25.943 --> 00:05:28.977
             HE'S NOT MY MASTER.
NO. OF COURSE NOT.

54
00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:31.379
WHAT HAPPENED HERE ?

55
00:05:31.448 --> 00:05:33.198
WHERE IS LADY STARK ?
WHY DIDN'T SHE RECEIVE ME ?

56
00:05:33.266 --> 00:05:36.334
        SHE WASN'T FEELING WELL.
SHE'S NOT IN WINTERFELL.
IS SHE ?

57
00:05:36.403 --> 00:05:38.236
WHERE DID SHE GO ?
         MY LADY'S WHEREABOUTS--

58
00:05:38.304 --> 00:05:39.721
MY LADY ? (Chuckles)

59
00:05:40.958 --> 00:05:44.025
YOUR LOYALTY TO YOUR
CAPTORS IS TOUCHING.

60
00:05:44.093 --> 00:05:47.012
TELL ME. HOW DO YOU THINK
BALON GREYJOY WOULD FEEL...

61
00:05:47.081 --> 00:05:50.815
IF HE COULD SEE HIS
ONLY SURVIVING SON
HAS TURNED LACKEY ?

62
00:05:50.884 --> 00:05:53.184
I STILL REMEMBER SEEING
MY FATHER'S FLEET...

63
00:05:53.253 --> 00:05:54.786
BURN IN LANNISPORT.

64
00:05:54.855 --> 00:05:56.971
I BELIEVE YOUR UNCLES
WERE RESPONSIBLE ?

65
00:05:57.040 --> 00:05:58.539
                 MUST HAVE BEEN
                 A PRETTY SIGHT.

66
00:05:58.608 --> 00:06:02.126
NOTHING PRETTIER THAN
WATCHING SAILORS BURN ALIVE.

67
00:06:02.196 --> 00:06:04.979
YES. A GREAT VICTORY
FOR YOUR PEOPLE.

68
00:06:05.048 --> 00:06:07.532
SHAME HOW IT ALL TURNED OUT.
WE WERE OUTNUMBERED TEN TO ONE--

69
00:06:07.601 --> 00:06:09.617
A STUPID REBELLION THEN.

70
00:06:09.686 --> 00:06:11.953
I SUPPOSE YOUR FATHER
REALIZED THAT...

71
00:06:12.039 --> 00:06:14.172
WHEN YOUR BROTHERS
DIED IN BATTLE.

72
00:06:14.241 --> 00:06:17.809
NOW HERE YOU ARE.
YOUR ENEMY'S SQUIRE.

73
00:06:17.878 --> 00:06:19.660
                   CAREFUL. IMP.
I'VE OFFENDED YOU.

74
00:06:20.914 --> 00:06:22.964
FORGIVE ME. IT'S BEEN
A ROUGH MORNING.

75
00:06:23.951 --> 00:06:26.217
ANYWAY. DON'T DESPAIR.

76
00:06:26.286 --> 00:06:28.620
I'M A CONSTANT
DISAPPOINTMENT
TO MY OWN FATHER...

77
00:06:28.689 --> 00:06:30.738
AND I'VE LEARNED
TO LIVE WITH IT.

78
00:06:30.807 --> 00:06:33.558
        (Coin clinks)
YOUR NEXT TUMBLE
WITH ROS IS ON ME.

79
00:06:34.778 --> 00:06:36.511
I'LL TRY NOT
TO WEAR HER OUT.

80
00:06:39.516 --> 00:06:41.282
           (Exhales)

81
00:06:41.368 --> 00:06:43.784
      Jon: SHOULDER. LEGS.

82
00:06:48.658 --> 00:06:51.759
      LEG. SHOULDER. LEG.

83
00:06:53.330 --> 00:06:55.113
       LEFT FOOT FORWARD.
       GOOD.

84
00:06:55.165 --> 00:06:57.265
      NOW PIVOT AS YOU
      DELIVER THE STROKE.

85
00:06:57.334 --> 00:06:59.100
      PUT ALL YOUR WEIGHT
      BEHIND IT.

86
00:06:59.169 --> 00:07:01.619
      WHAT IN SEVEN HELLS
      IS THAT ?

87
00:07:01.688 --> 00:07:04.105
   Pyp: THEY'LL NEED AN
   EIGHTH HELL TO FIT HIM IN.

88
00:07:04.174 --> 00:07:05.506
           (Laughter)

89
00:07:06.760 --> 00:07:08.309
TELL THEM YOUR NAME.

90
00:07:08.378 --> 00:07:10.462
       SAMWELL TARLY...

91
00:07:10.531 --> 00:07:11.997
OF HORN HILL--

92
00:07:12.065 --> 00:07:14.448
I MEAN.
I WAS OF HORN HILL.

93
00:07:14.518 --> 00:07:18.003
I'VE COME TO TAKE THE BLACK.
COME TO TAKE THE BLACK PUDDING.

94
00:07:18.055 --> 00:07:19.154
           (Laughter)

95
00:07:19.222 --> 00:07:22.089
        WELL. YOU COULDN'T BE
        ANY WORSE THAN YOU LOOK.

96
00:07:22.158 --> 00:07:23.207
            RAST...

97
00:07:24.111 --> 00:07:25.644
      SEE WHAT HE CAN DO.

98
00:07:31.285 --> 00:07:33.384
            (Yelps)

99
00:07:33.453 --> 00:07:35.854
     (Whimpers) I YIELD.

100
00:07:35.923 --> 00:07:38.656
      PLEASE. NO MORE !
        ON YOUR FEET.

101
00:07:38.725 --> 00:07:40.758
      PICK UP YOUR SWORD.

102
00:07:40.827 --> 00:07:43.210
        HIT HIM TILL HE
        FINDS HIS FEET.

103
00:07:44.364 --> 00:07:46.163
       (Samwell yelping)

104
00:07:50.770 --> 00:07:52.386
         (Whimpering)

105
00:07:52.473 --> 00:07:55.573
    IT SEEMS THEY'VE
    RUN SHORT OF POACHERS
    AND THIEVES DOWN SOUTH.

106
00:07:55.642 --> 00:07:58.409
NOW THEY SEND US
SQUEALING BLOODY PIGS.
                           JON !

107
00:07:58.479 --> 00:08:00.861
AGAIN. HARDER.
           (Snarls)

108
00:08:00.931 --> 00:08:02.747
      (Shrieks) I YIELD !

109
00:08:02.816 --> 00:08:04.415
            ENOUGH !

110
00:08:04.485 --> 00:08:06.117
       (Samwell sobbing)
                     HE YIELDED.

111
00:08:09.273 --> 00:08:10.938
       LOOKS LIKE THE
       BASTARD'S IN LOVE.

112
00:08:14.144 --> 00:08:15.910
        ALL RIGHT THEN.
        LORD SNOW...

113
00:08:15.979 --> 00:08:18.012
       YOU WISH TO DEFEND
       YOUR LADY LOVE...

114
00:08:18.081 --> 00:08:20.065
   LET'S MAKE IT AN EXERCISE.
   YOU TWO.

115
00:08:20.117 --> 00:08:22.217
THREE OF YOU OUGHT
TO BE SUFFICIENT...

116
00:08:22.285 --> 00:08:24.685
   TO MAKE LADY PIGGY SQUEAL.

117
00:08:24.755 --> 00:08:27.638
    ALL YOU'VE GOT TO DO
    IS GET PAST THE BASTARD.

118
00:08:30.109 --> 00:08:31.576
       ARE YOU SURE YOU
       WANT TO DO THIS ?

119
00:08:31.644 --> 00:08:32.661
              NO.

120
00:08:46.226 --> 00:08:48.793
     YIELD. YIELD. YIELD !
     I YIELD.

121
00:08:51.431 --> 00:08:53.231
     WE'RE DONE FOR TODAY.

122
00:08:53.300 --> 00:08:54.632
      GO CLEAN THE ARMORY.

123
00:08:54.701 --> 00:08:56.134
  THAT'S ALL YOU'RE GOOD FOR.

124
00:09:00.523 --> 00:09:02.857
                   WELL FOUGHT !
         PISS OFF.

125
00:09:04.161 --> 00:09:05.726
           (Spits)

126
00:09:06.947 --> 00:09:09.330
       DID HE HURT YOU ?

127
00:09:09.398 --> 00:09:10.598
I'VE HAD WORSE.

128
00:09:12.052 --> 00:09:14.768
          YOU CAN CALL ME SAM...
          IF YOU WANT.

129
00:09:14.838 --> 00:09:17.205
        MY MOTHER CALLS ME SAM--

130
00:09:17.273 --> 00:09:19.107
IT'S NOT GOING TO GET
ANY EASIER. YOU KNOW.

131
00:09:19.176 --> 00:09:20.675
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE
TO DEFEND YOURSELF.

132
00:09:20.761 --> 00:09:22.560
              WHY DIDN'T YOU GET
              UP AND FIGHT ?

133
00:09:23.746 --> 00:09:24.879
                    I WANTED TO.

134
00:09:26.115 --> 00:09:28.867
               I JUST COULDN'T.
       WHY NOT ?

135
00:09:30.503 --> 00:09:31.987
         I'M A COWARD.

136
00:09:33.890 --> 00:09:35.373
   MY FATHER ALWAYS SAYS SO.

137
00:09:35.442 --> 00:09:39.094
THE WALL'S NO PLACE FOR COWARDS.
        YOU'RE RIGHT. I'M SORRY.

138
00:09:39.162 --> 00:09:42.063
                 I JUST...WANTED
                 TO THANK YOU.

139
00:09:52.726 --> 00:09:54.776
        A BLOODY COWARD.

140
00:09:54.845 --> 00:09:57.111
        PEOPLE SAW US
        TALKING TO HIM.

141
00:09:57.180 --> 00:09:59.130
       NOW THEY'LL THINK
       WE'RE COWARDS TOO.

142
00:09:59.199 --> 00:10:00.865
       YOU'RE TOO STUPID
       TO BE A COWARD.

143
00:10:00.934 --> 00:10:03.034
YOU'RE TOO STUPID TO BE A--
                    QUICK NOW...

144
00:10:03.103 --> 00:10:05.303
           BEFORE SUMMER'S OVER.
           (Laughing)

145
00:10:06.873 --> 00:10:07.839
            C'MERE !

146
00:10:14.947 --> 00:10:16.648
        (Horse neighs)

147
00:10:36.302 --> 00:10:39.554
          (Neighing)
        HYAH ! HYAH !

148
00:10:42.059 --> 00:10:46.210
  Jorah: VAES DOTHRAK--
  THE CITY OF THE HORSELORDS.

149
00:10:48.148 --> 00:10:50.031
                  A PILE OF MUD.

150
00:10:50.099 --> 00:10:51.716
                    MUD AND SHIT
                    AND TWIGS--

151
00:10:51.768 --> 00:10:55.486
      BEST THESE SAVAGES CAN DO.
THESE ARE MY PEOPLE NOW.

152
00:10:55.555 --> 00:10:57.138
YOU SHOULDN'T
CALL THEM SAVAGES.

153
00:10:57.223 --> 00:10:59.757
     I'LL CALL THEM WHAT I LIKE.
     BECAUSE THEY'RE MY PEOPLE.

154
00:10:59.826 --> 00:11:01.826
                THIS IS MY ARMY.

155
00:11:01.895 --> 00:11:04.962
     KHAL DROGO IS MARCHING
     THE WRONG WAY WITH MY ARMY.

156
00:11:24.334 --> 00:11:28.736
         IF MY BROTHER WAS GIVEN
         AN ARMY OF DOTHRAKI...

157
00:11:28.805 --> 00:11:31.172
            COULD YOU CONQUER
            THE SEVEN KINGDOMS ?

158
00:11:31.240 --> 00:11:34.074
THE DOTHRAKI HAVE NEVER
CROSSED THE NARROW SEA.

159
00:11:34.144 --> 00:11:36.577
THEY FEAR ANY WATER
THEIR HORSES CAN'T DRINK.

160
00:11:36.646 --> 00:11:37.895
               BUT IF THEY DID ?

161
00:11:39.733 --> 00:11:43.301
 KING ROBERT IS FOOL ENOUGH
 TO MEET THEM IN OPEN BATTLE...

162
00:11:43.369 --> 00:11:45.436
BUT THE MEN ADVISING
HIM ARE DIFFERENT.

163
00:11:45.505 --> 00:11:49.791
        AND YOU KNOW THESE MEN ?
I FOUGHT BESIDE THEM ONCE...

164
00:11:49.876 --> 00:11:52.042
LONG AGO.

165
00:11:52.111 --> 00:11:54.378
  NOW NED STARK WANTS MY HEAD.

166
00:11:54.447 --> 00:11:56.547
HE DROVE ME
FROM MY LAND.

167
00:11:58.751 --> 00:12:00.351
                YOU SOLD SLAVES.

168
00:12:01.922 --> 00:12:03.021
              AYE.

169
00:12:05.308 --> 00:12:08.276
             WHY ?
       I HAD NO MONEY...

170
00:12:08.344 --> 00:12:10.611
AND AN EXPENSIVE WIFE.

171
00:12:10.680 --> 00:12:12.180
          AND WHERE IS SHE NOW ?

172
00:12:12.248 --> 00:12:14.548
IN ANOTHER PLACE...

173
00:12:14.617 --> 00:12:16.050
WITH ANOTHER MAN.

174
00:12:23.259 --> 00:12:25.242
         YOUR GRACE ?
                  YES. MY DEAR ?

175
00:12:25.311 --> 00:12:27.995
       THEY CALL YOU
       THE LAST DRAGON.

176
00:12:28.081 --> 00:12:29.280
                        THEY DO.

177
00:12:32.068 --> 00:12:34.185
       YOU HAVE
       DRAGON'S BLOOD...

178
00:12:34.254 --> 00:12:36.287
        IN YOUR VEINS ?

179
00:12:36.356 --> 00:12:38.239
                   IT'S ENTIRELY
                   POSSIBLE.

180
00:12:38.324 --> 00:12:41.743
    (Chuckles) WHAT HAPPENED
    TO THE DRAGONS ?

181
00:12:41.811 --> 00:12:44.795
I WAS TOLD THAT BRAVE MEN
KILLED THEM ALL.

182
00:12:48.568 --> 00:12:52.169
            THE BRAVE MEN
            DIDN'T KILL DRAGONS.

183
00:12:52.238 --> 00:12:54.672
                   THE BRAVE MEN
                   RODE THEM.

184
00:12:54.741 --> 00:12:58.125
          RODE THEM FROM VALYRIA
          TO BUILD THE GREATEST
          CIVILIZATION...

185
00:12:58.194 --> 00:13:00.678
                  THIS WORLD HAS
                  EVER SEEN.

186
00:13:00.730 --> 00:13:02.930
              THE BREATH OF THE
              GREATEST DRAGON...

187
00:13:02.998 --> 00:13:05.233
       FORGED THE IRON THRONE...

188
00:13:05.301 --> 00:13:07.702
            WHICH THE USURPER IS
            KEEPING WARM FOR ME.

189
00:13:09.505 --> 00:13:12.439
               THE SWORDS OF
               THE VANQUISHED...

190
00:13:12.508 --> 00:13:14.441
                      A THOUSAND
                      OF THEM...

191
00:13:14.510 --> 00:13:18.913
           MELTED TOGETHER
           LIKE SO MANY CANDLES.

192
00:13:22.451 --> 00:13:25.219
      I HAVE ALWAYS WANTED
      TO SEE A DRAGON.

193
00:13:27.156 --> 00:13:29.823
      THERE IS NOTHING
      IN THE WORLD THAT
      I WOULD RATHER SEE.

194
00:13:29.893 --> 00:13:33.127
                   REALLY.
                   WHY DRAGONS ?

195
00:13:33.196 --> 00:13:34.895
         THEY CAN FLY.

196
00:13:34.981 --> 00:13:38.148
     AND WHEREVER THEY ARE.
     JUST A FEW FLAPS OF
     THEIR WINGS...

197
00:13:38.217 --> 00:13:40.718
       AND THEY'RE
       SOMEWHERE ELSE...

198
00:13:40.786 --> 00:13:42.653
           FAR AWAY.

199
00:13:45.291 --> 00:13:47.624
     AND THEY CAN KILL.

200
00:13:47.694 --> 00:13:50.662
     ANYONE OR ANYTHING...

201
00:13:50.730 --> 00:13:54.765
    THAT TRIES TO HURT THEM
    GETS BURNED AWAY...

202
00:13:54.834 --> 00:13:56.767
         TO NOTHING...
                         (Gasps)

203
00:13:56.836 --> 00:14:01.422
...MELTED...
LIKE SO MANY CANDLES.

204
00:14:01.491 --> 00:14:02.623
                             OW.

205
00:14:04.894 --> 00:14:06.994
       YES.
       SEEING A DRAGON...

206
00:14:07.063 --> 00:14:08.996
   WOULD MAKE ME VERY HAPPY.

207
00:14:09.082 --> 00:14:11.315
          WELL. AFTER 15 YEARS
          IN A PLEASURE HOUSE...

208
00:14:11.384 --> 00:14:13.551
        I IMAGINE JUST SEEING
        THE SKY MAKES YOU HAPPY.

209
00:14:13.619 --> 00:14:16.787
I WAS NOT LOCKED IN.
I HAVE SEEN THINGS.

210
00:14:16.856 --> 00:14:18.572
            WHAT HAVE YOU SEEN ?
I'VE SEEN...

211
00:14:18.642 --> 00:14:22.744
A MAN FROM ASSHAI WITH A
DAGGER OF REAL DRAGONGLASS.

212
00:14:22.812 --> 00:14:24.729
                            OOH.
I'VE SEEN A MAN WHO COULD...

213
00:14:24.797 --> 00:14:26.330
CHANGE HIS FACE...

214
00:14:26.399 --> 00:14:29.366
THE WAY THAT OTHER MEN
CHANGE THEIR CLOTHES.

215
00:14:29.435 --> 00:14:33.271
AND I'VE SEEN A PIRATE WHO
WORE HIS WEIGHT IN GOLD...

216
00:14:33.339 --> 00:14:37.508
AND WHOSE SHIP HAD
SAILS OF COLORED SILK.

217
00:14:38.911 --> 00:14:40.111
             SO...

218
00:14:42.515 --> 00:14:44.732
HAVE YOU SEEN ONE ?

219
00:14:44.801 --> 00:14:47.685
                 A PIRATE SHIP ?
A DRAGON.

220
00:14:48.854 --> 00:14:49.870
                             NO.

221
00:14:51.240 --> 00:14:54.174
      NO. THE LAST ONE DIED MANY
      YEARS BEFORE I WAS BORN.

222
00:14:55.378 --> 00:14:57.044
              I'LL TELL YOU WHAT
              I HAVE SEEN--

223
00:14:58.682 --> 00:15:00.898
                   THEIR SKULLS.

224
00:15:00.967 --> 00:15:04.068
    THEY USED TO DECORATE THE
    THRONE ROOM IN THE RED KEEP.

225
00:15:04.137 --> 00:15:05.669
          WHEN I WAS VERY YOUNG.
          JUST THREE OR FOUR...

226
00:15:05.738 --> 00:15:08.038
          MY FATHER USED TO WALK
          ME DOWN THE ROWS...

227
00:15:08.108 --> 00:15:10.575
            AND I'D RECITE
            THEIR NAMES FOR HIM.

228
00:15:10.643 --> 00:15:14.479
      WHEN I GOT THEM ALL RIGHT.
      HE'D GIVE ME A SWEET.

229
00:15:14.547 --> 00:15:17.348
    THE ONES CLOSEST TO THE DOOR
    WERE THE LAST ONES THEY
    WERE ABLE TO HATCH...

230
00:15:17.417 --> 00:15:19.083
              AND THEY WERE ALL
              STUNTED AND WRONG.

231
00:15:19.152 --> 00:15:23.454
                SKULLS NO BIGGER
                THAN DOG SKULLS.

232
00:15:23.523 --> 00:15:27.525
           BUT AS YOU GOT CLOSER
           TO THE IRON THRONE...

233
00:15:28.962 --> 00:15:31.029
              THEY GOT BIGGER...

234
00:15:31.097 --> 00:15:34.364
          AND BIGGER AND BIGGER.

235
00:15:37.169 --> 00:15:39.536
            THERE WAS GHISCAR...

236
00:15:39.606 --> 00:15:42.039
                  AND VALRYON...

237
00:15:42.108 --> 00:15:43.874
                   VERMITHRAX...

238
00:15:43.943 --> 00:15:46.010
              ESSOVIUS-- (Gasps)

239
00:15:46.079 --> 00:15:48.662
                     ARCHONEI...

240
00:15:48.732 --> 00:15:51.498
                      MERAXES...

241
00:15:53.502 --> 00:15:54.985
                       VHAGAR...

242
00:15:56.889 --> 00:16:00.024
       AND BALERION THE DREAD...
           (Moans)

243
00:16:00.093 --> 00:16:02.326
         ...WHOSE FIRE FORGED...

244
00:16:02.394 --> 00:16:04.461
           THE SEVEN KINGDOMS...

245
00:16:04.530 --> 00:16:06.597
                       INTO ONE.

246
00:16:11.404 --> 00:16:13.804
WHAT HAPPENED
TO THE SKULLS ?

247
00:16:16.108 --> 00:16:17.875
                   I DON'T KNOW.

248
00:16:17.943 --> 00:16:21.011
            THE USURPER HAD THEM
            SMASHED TO POWDER.
            I EXPECT.

249
00:16:22.081 --> 00:16:24.114
          SCATTERED TO THE WIND.

250
00:16:27.287 --> 00:16:28.919
THAT'S VERY SAD.

251
00:16:30.056 --> 00:16:31.723
                     YES. IT IS.

252
00:16:33.493 --> 00:16:35.360
                   WHAT DID I
                   BUY YOU FOR ?

253
00:16:35.428 --> 00:16:38.162
                TO MAKE ME SAD ?
NO. YOUR GRACE.

254
00:16:39.699 --> 00:16:43.133
TO. UH.
TEACH YOUR SISTER.

255
00:16:43.202 --> 00:16:46.270
          TO TEACH MY SISTER HOW
          TO BE A BETTER LOVER ?

256
00:16:46.339 --> 00:16:49.407
       YOU THINK I BOUGHT YOU TO
       MAKE KHAL DROGO HAPPY ?

257
00:16:54.213 --> 00:16:56.214
                  OH. YOU PRETTY
                  LITTLE IDIOT.

258
00:16:56.949 --> 00:16:58.849
                      (Chuckles)

259
00:16:58.918 --> 00:17:00.551
                 GO ON THEN.
                 GET ON WITH IT.

260
00:17:10.996 --> 00:17:14.298
SOMEDAY YOUR HUSBAND
WILL SIT THERE...

261
00:17:14.367 --> 00:17:15.916
AND YOU WILL SIT
BY HIS SIDE.

262
00:17:15.985 --> 00:17:18.552
              AND ONE DAY.
              BEFORE TOO LONG...

263
00:17:18.621 --> 00:17:21.755
          YOU WILL PRESENT
          YOUR SON TO THE COURT.

264
00:17:21.824 --> 00:17:23.640
                  ALL THE LORDS
                  OF WESTEROS...

265
00:17:23.709 --> 00:17:26.393
    WILL GATHER HERE TO SEE
    THE LITTLE PRINCE--

266
00:17:26.463 --> 00:17:27.829
WHAT IF I
HAVE A GIRL ?

267
00:17:27.897 --> 00:17:30.130
               GODS BE GOOD.
               YOU'LL HAVE
               BOYS AND GIRLS...

268
00:17:30.199 --> 00:17:31.699
             AND PLENTY OF THEM.

269
00:17:31.768 --> 00:17:34.001
WHAT IF I ONLY
HAVE GIRLS ?

270
00:17:34.070 --> 00:17:36.153
                I WOULDN'T WORRY
                ABOUT THAT.

271
00:17:36.222 --> 00:17:39.123
JEYNE POOLE'S MOTHER
HAD FIVE CHILDREN--
ALL OF THEM GIRLS.

272
00:17:39.191 --> 00:17:41.425
                YES. BUT IT'S
                HIGHLY UNLIKELY.

273
00:17:41.493 --> 00:17:42.659
BUT WHAT IF ?

274
00:17:43.896 --> 00:17:47.147
               WELL. IF YOU ONLY
               HAD GIRLS...

275
00:17:47.216 --> 00:17:51.335
      I SUPPOSE THE THRONE WOULD
      PASS TO PRINCE JOFFREY'S
      LITTLE BROTHER.

276
00:17:51.403 --> 00:17:54.221
AND EVERYONE
WOULD HATE ME.

277
00:17:54.290 --> 00:17:56.156
                  NOBODY COULD
                  EVER HATE YOU.

278
00:17:56.225 --> 00:17:58.725
JOFFREY DOES.
                       NONSENSE.

279
00:17:58.794 --> 00:18:01.446
               WHY WOULD YOU SAY
               SUCH A THING ?

280
00:18:02.999 --> 00:18:04.532
               THAT BUSINESS
               WITH THE WOLVES ?

281
00:18:04.600 --> 00:18:07.167
            SANSA. I'VE TOLD YOU
            A HUNDRED TIMES--

282
00:18:07.236 --> 00:18:09.953
             A DIREWOLF IS NOT--
PLEASE SHUT UP ABOUT IT.

283
00:18:12.058 --> 00:18:14.024
       DO YOU REMEMBER
       YOUR LESSONS ?

284
00:18:15.144 --> 00:18:18.412
  WHO BUILT THE IRON THRONE ?

285
00:18:18.480 --> 00:18:20.314
      AEGON THE CONQUEROR.

286
00:18:20.382 --> 00:18:22.183
         AND WHO BUILT
         THE RED KEEP ?

287
00:18:22.251 --> 00:18:23.751
       MAEGOR THE CRUEL.

288
00:18:23.836 --> 00:18:25.669
     AND HOW MANY YEARS
     DID IT TAKE TO BUILD--

289
00:18:25.722 --> 00:18:28.489
        MY GRANDFATHER AND UNCLE
        WERE MURDERED HERE.
        WEREN'T THEY ?

290
00:18:30.443 --> 00:18:34.077
THEY WERE KILLED
ON THE ORDERS OF
KING AERYS. YES.

291
00:18:34.147 --> 00:18:37.698
                   THE MAD KING.
COMMONLY KNOWN AS THE MAD KING.

292
00:18:38.685 --> 00:18:39.850
          WHY WERE THEY KILLED ?

293
00:18:41.654 --> 00:18:44.471
  YOU SHOULD SPEAK TO YOUR
  FATHER ABOUT THESE MATTERS.

294
00:18:44.540 --> 00:18:46.524
           I DON'T WANT TO SPEAK
           TO MY FATHER. EVER.

295
00:18:46.592 --> 00:18:49.927
SANSA. YOU WILL FIND
IT IN YOUR HEART...

296
00:18:49.996 --> 00:18:51.962
TO FORGIVE YOUR FATHER.

297
00:18:52.031 --> 00:18:53.464
                    NO. I WON'T.

298
00:18:53.533 --> 00:18:56.000
  Man: IT'S THE HAND'S
  TOURNAMENT THAT'S CAUSING...

299
00:18:56.068 --> 00:18:58.869
ALL THIS TROUBLE. MY LORDS.
  THE KING'S TOURNAMENT.

300
00:18:58.938 --> 00:19:02.506
     I ASSURE YOU. THE HAND
     WANTS NO PART OF IT.

301
00:19:02.575 --> 00:19:04.792
     CALL IT WHAT YOU WILL.
     LORD STARK. SER.

302
00:19:04.861 --> 00:19:08.329
     THE CITY IS PACKED
     WITH PEOPLE AND MORE
     FLOODING IN EVERY DAY.

303
00:19:08.397 --> 00:19:10.882
LAST NIGHT WE HAD A TAVERN RIOT.
A BROTHEL FIRE...

304
00:19:10.950 --> 00:19:12.850
    THREE STABBINGS AND A
    DRUNKEN HORSE RACE...

305
00:19:12.918 --> 00:19:15.002
  DOWN THE STREET OF SISTERS.
                       DREADFUL.

306
00:19:15.071 --> 00:19:16.737
IF YOU CAN'T KEEP
THE KING'S PEACE...

307
00:19:16.806 --> 00:19:19.707
PERHAPS THE CITY WATCH
SHOULD BE COMMANDED
BY SOMEONE WHO CAN.

308
00:19:19.776 --> 00:19:21.492
                I NEED MORE MEN.
      Ned: YOU'LL GET 50.

309
00:19:21.561 --> 00:19:23.160
       LORD BAELISH WILL
       SEE IT PAID FOR.

310
00:19:23.229 --> 00:19:24.395
                        I WILL ?

311
00:19:24.463 --> 00:19:26.147
      YOU FOUND MONEY FOR
      A CHAMPION'S PURSE.

312
00:19:26.215 --> 00:19:28.165
       YOU CAN FIND MONEY
       TO KEEP THE PEACE.

313
00:19:30.536 --> 00:19:32.519
    I'LL ALSO GIVE YOU 20
    OF MY HOUSEHOLD GUARD...

314
00:19:32.589 --> 00:19:34.021
   TILL THE CROWDS HAVE LEFT.

315
00:19:34.090 --> 00:19:35.606
              THANK YOU.
              MY LORD HAND. SER.

316
00:19:35.675 --> 00:19:37.007
                THEY WILL BE PUT
                TO GOOD USE.

317
00:19:39.745 --> 00:19:41.578
    THE SOONER THIS IS OVER.
    THE BETTER.

318
00:19:41.647 --> 00:19:44.514
   THE REALM PROSPERS
   FROM SUCH EVENTS. MY LORD.

319
00:19:44.583 --> 00:19:46.383
      THEY GIVE THE GREAT
      A CHANCE AT GLORY...

320
00:19:46.452 --> 00:19:48.669
    AND THE LOWLY A RESPITE
    FROM THEIR WOES.

321
00:19:48.738 --> 00:19:51.471
     Baelish: AND EVERY INN
     IN THE CITY IS FULL...

322
00:19:51.558 --> 00:19:53.507
    AND THE WHORES
    ARE WALKING BOW-LEGGED.

323
00:19:53.575 --> 00:19:56.193
  I'M SURE THE TOURNEY
  PUTS COINS IN MANY A POCKET.

324
00:19:56.262 --> 00:19:58.745
             HMMM.
            NOW...

325
00:19:58.815 --> 00:20:01.298
    IF THERE'S NOTHING ELSE.
    MY LORDS ?

326
00:20:11.093 --> 00:20:13.026
OH. THIS HEAT.

327
00:20:13.095 --> 00:20:16.129
       ON DAYS LIKE THIS.
       I ENVY YOU NORTHERNERS...

328
00:20:16.198 --> 00:20:19.099
       YOUR SUMMER SNOWS.
       UNTIL TOMORROW. MY LORD--

329
00:20:19.168 --> 00:20:21.385
    I'VE BEEN HOPING TO TALK
    TO YOU ABOUT JON ARRYN.

330
00:20:22.738 --> 00:20:24.338
                    LORD ARRYN ?

331
00:20:24.424 --> 00:20:26.824
            OH. HIS DEATH WAS...

332
00:20:26.893 --> 00:20:29.326
                 A GREAT SADNESS
                 TO ALL OF US.

333
00:20:29.395 --> 00:20:31.578
     I TOOK PERSONAL CHARGE
     OF HIS CARE...

334
00:20:31.647 --> 00:20:34.514
       BUT I COULD NOT SAVE HIM.

335
00:20:34.583 --> 00:20:36.817
   HIS SICKNESS STRUCK HIM...

336
00:20:36.886 --> 00:20:40.154
    VERY HARD AND VERY FAST.

337
00:20:41.224 --> 00:20:42.890
  I SAW HIM IN MY CHAMBERS...

338
00:20:42.958 --> 00:20:44.624
       JUST THE NIGHT
       BEFORE HE PASSED.

339
00:20:44.693 --> 00:20:47.811
             LORD JON OFTEN CAME
             TO ME FOR COUNSEL.

340
00:20:47.880 --> 00:20:49.513
             WHY ?

341
00:20:51.550 --> 00:20:54.585
       I HAVE BEEN GRAND MAESTER
       FOR MANY YEARS.

342
00:20:54.654 --> 00:20:57.822
       KINGS AND HANDS HAVE COME
       TO ME FOR ADVICE SINCE--

343
00:20:57.890 --> 00:21:00.607
WHAT DID JON WANT.
THE NIGHT BEFORE HE DIED ?

344
00:21:00.676 --> 00:21:03.343
           OH. HE CAME INQUIRING
           AFTER A BOOK.

345
00:21:03.412 --> 00:21:04.811
A BOOK ?

346
00:21:04.880 --> 00:21:06.530
WHAT BOOK ?

347
00:21:06.599 --> 00:21:08.399
                   OH. I FEAR...

348
00:21:08.468 --> 00:21:11.102
       IT WOULD BE OF LITTLE
       INTEREST TO YOU. MY LORD.

349
00:21:11.170 --> 00:21:13.553
               A PONDEROUS TOME.

350
00:21:13.640 --> 00:21:16.540
NO. I'D LIKE TO READ IT.

351
00:21:17.993 --> 00:21:22.763
 THE LINEAGES AND HISTORIES...

352
00:21:22.832 --> 00:21:26.066
    OF THE GREAT HOUSES
    OF THE SEVEN KINGDOMS...

353
00:21:26.135 --> 00:21:29.820
     WITH DESCRIPTIONS
     OF MANY HIGH LORDS...

354
00:21:29.888 --> 00:21:32.123
      AND NOBLE LADIES...

355
00:21:32.191 --> 00:21:34.224
      AND THEIR CHILDREN.

356
00:21:51.593 --> 00:21:53.961
      "HARKON UMBER.
      FIRST OF HIS NAME...

357
00:21:54.029 --> 00:21:57.865
  "BORN TO LORD HOTHER UMBER
  AND LADY AMARYLLIS UMBER...

358
00:21:57.934 --> 00:22:01.085
    "IN THE 183rd YEAR
    AFTER AEGON'S LANDING...

359
00:22:01.153 --> 00:22:03.687
 "AT THE LAST HEARTH.
 BLUE OF EYE. BROWN OF HAIR...

360
00:22:03.755 --> 00:22:07.274
    "AND FAIR COMPLECTED.
    DIED IN HIS 14th YEAR...

361
00:22:07.343 --> 00:22:09.876
     "OF A WOUND SUSTAINED
     IN A BEAR HUNT."

362
00:22:09.945 --> 00:22:13.363
      AS I SAID. MY LORD.
      A PONDEROUS READ.

363
00:22:13.416 --> 00:22:16.166
    DID JON ARRYN TELL YOU
    WHAT HE WANTED WITH IT ?

364
00:22:16.235 --> 00:22:18.986
 HE DID NOT. MY LORD.
 AND I DID NOT PRESUME TO ASK.

365
00:22:19.054 --> 00:22:21.405
        JON'S DEATH...
        SUCH A TRAGEDY.

366
00:22:21.473 --> 00:22:23.857
 ...DID HE SAY ANYTHING TO YOU
 DURING HIS FINAL HOURS ?

367
00:22:23.926 --> 00:22:25.842
       NOTHING OF IMPORT.
       MY LORD.

368
00:22:25.911 --> 00:22:28.679
         OH--
         THERE WAS ONE PHRASE...

369
00:22:28.748 --> 00:22:30.881
            HE KEPT REPEATING...

370
00:22:30.949 --> 00:22:34.185
           "THE SEED IS STRONG."
           I THINK IT WAS.

371
00:22:34.253 --> 00:22:36.570
"THE SEED IS STRONG" ?
                            MMM.

372
00:22:36.639 --> 00:22:38.705
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN ?
                           OH...

373
00:22:38.774 --> 00:22:42.409
      THE DYING MIND IS A
      DEMENTED MIND. LORD STARK.

374
00:22:42.477 --> 00:22:44.812
              FOR ALL THE WEIGHT
              THEY'RE GIVEN...

375
00:22:44.880 --> 00:22:46.546
                  LAST WORDS ARE
                  USUALLY...

376
00:22:46.615 --> 00:22:48.532
                 AS SIGNIFICANT
                 AS FIRST WORDS.

377
00:22:48.601 --> 00:22:51.769
  AND YOU'RE QUITE CERTAIN HE
  DIED OF A NATURAL ILLNESS ?

378
00:22:51.838 --> 00:22:54.004
         WHAT ELSE COULD IT BE ?

379
00:22:54.807 --> 00:22:55.806
            POISON.

380
00:22:57.192 --> 00:22:58.892
           A DISTURBING THOUGHT.

381
00:22:58.961 --> 00:23:01.662
             NO. NO. NO. I DON'T
             THINK IT LIKELY.

382
00:23:01.730 --> 00:23:04.097
               THE HAND
               WAS LOVED BY ALL.

383
00:23:04.166 --> 00:23:05.833
                WHAT SORT OF MAN
                WOULD DARE--

384
00:23:05.918 --> 00:23:08.668
I'VE HEARD IT
SAID THAT POISON
IS A WOMAN'S WEAPON.

385
00:23:08.755 --> 00:23:11.255
                   YES. WOMEN...

386
00:23:11.323 --> 00:23:13.357
                      CRAVENS...

387
00:23:13.425 --> 00:23:14.842
                    AND EUNUCHS.

388
00:23:16.378 --> 00:23:19.229
        DID YOU KNOW THAT
        LORD VARYS IS A EUNUCH ?

389
00:23:19.298 --> 00:23:20.714
EVERYBODY KNOWS THAT.

390
00:23:20.783 --> 00:23:23.684
            YES. YES. OF COURSE.

391
00:23:23.752 --> 00:23:26.520
        HOW THAT SORT OF PERSON
        FOUND HIMSELF...

392
00:23:26.588 --> 00:23:29.089
          ON THE KING'S COUNCIL.
          I WILL NEVER KNOW.

393
00:23:29.158 --> 00:23:30.907
       I'VE TAKEN ENOUGH
       OF YOUR TIME.

394
00:23:30.976 --> 00:23:33.543
     NO TROUBLE AT ALL. MY LORD.
     IT'S A GREAT HONOR--

395
00:23:33.613 --> 00:23:35.445
           THANK YOU.

396
00:23:35.514 --> 00:23:37.180
   I'LL FIND MY OWN WAY OUT.

397
00:23:47.609 --> 00:23:49.693
    (Footsteps approaching)

398
00:23:59.939 --> 00:24:01.839
        SYRIO SAYS A
        WATER DANCER...

399
00:24:01.908 --> 00:24:04.341
CAN STAND ON ONE
TOE FOR HOURS.

400
00:24:04.410 --> 00:24:06.360
               IT'S A HARD FALL
               DOWN THESE STEPS.

401
00:24:06.428 --> 00:24:08.795
SYRIO SAYS EVERY
HURT IS A LESSON...

402
00:24:08.865 --> 00:24:10.431
AND EVERY LESSON
MAKES YOU BETTER.

403
00:24:12.101 --> 00:24:14.067
TOMORROW I'M GOING
TO BE CHASING CATS.

404
00:24:14.136 --> 00:24:16.670
                     CATS ?
                     SYRIO SAYS.

405
00:24:16.739 --> 00:24:18.822
    HE SAYS EVERY SWORDSMAN
    SHOULD STUDY CATS.

406
00:24:18.890 --> 00:24:21.875
THEY'RE QUIET AS SHADOWS
AND AS LIGHT AS FEATHERS.

407
00:24:21.944 --> 00:24:24.144
      YOU HAVE TO BE
      QUICK TO CATCH THEM.

408
00:24:24.213 --> 00:24:26.013
          HE'S RIGHT ABOUT THAT.

409
00:24:26.082 --> 00:24:27.498
NOW THAT BRAN'S AWAKE...

410
00:24:28.534 --> 00:24:30.601
WILL HE COME LIVE WITH US ?

411
00:24:32.304 --> 00:24:35.789
        WELL. HE NEEDS TO GET
        HIS STRENGTH BACK FIRST.

412
00:24:35.858 --> 00:24:37.924
    HE WANTS TO BE A KNIGHT
    OF THE KINGSGUARD.

413
00:24:38.010 --> 00:24:42.062
HE CAN'T BE ONE NOW. CAN HE ?
             NO.

414
00:24:44.050 --> 00:24:46.050
                  BUT SOMEDAY...

415
00:24:46.118 --> 00:24:48.518
                HE COULD BE LORD
                OF A HOLDFAST...

416
00:24:48.587 --> 00:24:51.689
                 OR SIT ON THE
                 KING'S COUNCIL.

417
00:24:51.757 --> 00:24:53.691
                OR HE MIGHT
                RAISE CASTLES...

418
00:24:53.759 --> 00:24:56.493
                    LIKE BRANDON
                    THE BUILDER.

419
00:24:56.562 --> 00:24:58.762
CAN I BE LORD
OF A HOLDFAST ?

420
00:24:58.831 --> 00:25:00.998
                      (Chuckles)

421
00:25:03.235 --> 00:25:05.635
                  YOU WILL MARRY
                  A HIGH LORD...

422
00:25:05.705 --> 00:25:07.805
                     AND RULE
                     HIS CASTLE.

423
00:25:07.873 --> 00:25:10.407
             AND YOUR SONS
             SHALL BE KNIGHTS...

424
00:25:10.475 --> 00:25:12.609
                     AND PRINCES
                     AND LORDS.

425
00:25:14.847 --> 00:25:16.279
                           HMM ?
             NO.

426
00:25:18.283 --> 00:25:20.784
         THAT'S NOT ME.

427
00:25:30.679 --> 00:25:32.946
        (Wind gusting)

428
00:25:43.058 --> 00:25:44.024
                          HELLO.

429
00:25:46.212 --> 00:25:49.145
      SER ALLISER SAID I'M TO
      BE YOUR NEW WATCH PARTNER.

430
00:25:51.049 --> 00:25:53.016
            I SHOULD WARN YOU...

431
00:25:53.085 --> 00:25:55.752
                  I DON'T SEE
                  ALL THAT WELL.

432
00:25:57.089 --> 00:26:00.524
COME STAND BY THE FIRE.
IT'S WARMER.

433
00:26:00.593 --> 00:26:01.908
           NO. THAT'S ALL RIGHT.
           I'M FINE.

434
00:26:01.977 --> 00:26:03.977
YOU'RE NOT.
YOU'RE FREEZING.

435
00:26:16.925 --> 00:26:18.492
                    I DON'T LIKE
                    HIGH PLACES.

436
00:26:19.462 --> 00:26:21.362
YOU CAN'T FIGHT.

437
00:26:21.430 --> 00:26:23.497
YOU CAN'T SEE.

438
00:26:23.565 --> 00:26:26.683
YOU'RE AFRAID OF HEIGHTS.
AND ALMOST EVERYTHING
ELSE. PROBABLY.

439
00:26:28.421 --> 00:26:30.321
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE. SAM ?

440
00:26:34.927 --> 00:26:39.296
           ON THE MORNING
           OF MY 18th NAMEDAY.
           MY FATHER CAME TO ME.

441
00:26:39.365 --> 00:26:42.967
          "YOU'RE ALMOST
          A MAN NOW." HE SAID...

442
00:26:43.035 --> 00:26:47.438
          "BUT YOU'RE NOT WORTHY
          OF MY LAND AND TITLE.

443
00:26:47.506 --> 00:26:49.873
         "TOMORROW. YOU'RE GOING
         TO TAKE THE BLACK...

444
00:26:49.942 --> 00:26:53.110
             "FORSAKE ALL CLAIM
             TO YOUR INHERITANCE
             AND START NORTH.

445
00:26:54.230 --> 00:26:58.665
                "IF YOU DO NOT."
                HE SAID...

446
00:26:58.734 --> 00:27:01.168
                  "THEN WE'LL
                  HAVE A HUNT...

447
00:27:01.236 --> 00:27:04.304
   "AND SOMEWHERE IN THESE WOODS
   YOUR HORSE WILL STUMBLE...

448
00:27:04.372 --> 00:27:07.074
        "AND YOU'LL BE THROWN
        FROM YOUR SADDLE TO DIE.

449
00:27:09.361 --> 00:27:12.162
                "OR SO I'LL TELL
                YOUR MOTHER.

450
00:27:12.230 --> 00:27:13.763
                "NOTHING WOULD
                PLEASE ME MORE."

451
00:27:19.605 --> 00:27:22.606
SER ALLISER'S GOING TO MAKE ME
FIGHT AGAIN TOMORROW. ISN'T HE ?

452
00:27:23.775 --> 00:27:26.477
YES. HE IS.
                         (Moans)

453
00:27:26.545 --> 00:27:28.128
           I'M NOT GOING TO GET
           ANY BETTER. YOU KNOW.

454
00:27:29.798 --> 00:27:31.598
            WELL...

455
00:27:31.667 --> 00:27:33.834
    YOU CAN'T GET ANY WORSE.

456
00:27:35.754 --> 00:27:37.671
          (Chuckling)

457
00:27:43.329 --> 00:27:46.596
           I HEAR YOU'RE READING
           A BORING BOOK.

458
00:27:46.665 --> 00:27:48.398
HMPH.

459
00:27:48.467 --> 00:27:50.000
PYCELLE TALKS TOO MUCH.

460
00:27:50.069 --> 00:27:52.018
             OH. HE NEVER STOPS.

461
00:27:52.087 --> 00:27:55.589
            DO YOU KNOW SER HUGH
            OF THE VALE ?

462
00:27:55.657 --> 00:27:57.991
               NOT SURPRISING.
               UNTIL RECENTLY...

463
00:27:58.059 --> 00:28:01.662
          HE WAS ONLY A SQUIRE--
          JON ARRYN'S SQUIRE.

464
00:28:01.730 --> 00:28:03.696
           HE WAS KNIGHTED
           ALMOST IMMEDIATELY...

465
00:28:03.766 --> 00:28:06.549
              AFTER HIS MASTER'S
              UNTIMELY DEATH.

466
00:28:06.618 --> 00:28:10.821
KNIGHTED FOR WHAT ?
WHY ARE YOU TELLING ME THIS ?

467
00:28:10.890 --> 00:28:12.723
              I PROMISED CAT
              THAT I'D HELP YOU.

468
00:28:12.791 --> 00:28:15.659
WHERE IS SER HUGH ?

469
00:28:15.728 --> 00:28:18.061
I'LL SPEAK TO HIM.
          A SINGULARLY BAD IDEA.

470
00:28:18.129 --> 00:28:20.497
                 DO YOU SEE THAT
                 BOY THERE ?

471
00:28:20.566 --> 00:28:23.183
     (Whispers) ONE OF
     VARYS'S LITTLE BIRDS.

472
00:28:23.252 --> 00:28:26.953
        THE SPIDER HAS TAKEN
        A GREAT INTEREST IN
        YOUR COMINGS AND GOINGS.

473
00:28:27.022 --> 00:28:28.855
                NOW LOOK. THERE.

474
00:28:28.924 --> 00:28:32.058
                THAT ONE BELONGS
                TO THE QUEEN.

475
00:28:32.127 --> 00:28:36.162
           AND DO YOU SEE
           THAT SEPTA PRETENDING
           TO READ HER BOOK ?

476
00:28:36.248 --> 00:28:37.748
VARYS OR THE QUEEN ?

477
00:28:37.816 --> 00:28:40.851
          NO. SHE'S ONE OF MINE.

478
00:28:42.538 --> 00:28:46.122
IS THERE SOMEONE IN YOUR SERVICE
WHOM YOU TRUST COMPLETELY ?

479
00:28:47.626 --> 00:28:48.725
YES.

480
00:28:48.794 --> 00:28:51.678
                THE WISER ANSWER
                WAS NO. MY LORD.

481
00:28:51.747 --> 00:28:54.981
         GET A MESSAGE TO
         THIS PARAGON OF YOURS--

482
00:28:55.050 --> 00:28:58.969
           DISCREETLY-- SEND HIM
           TO QUESTION SER HUGH.

483
00:28:59.038 --> 00:29:03.089
      AFTER THAT. YOU MIGHT WANT
      HIM TO VISIT A CERTAIN
      ARMORER IN THE CITY.

484
00:29:03.158 --> 00:29:05.892
            HE LIVES IN A LARGE
            HOUSE AT THE TOP OF
            THE STREET OF STEEL.

485
00:29:05.961 --> 00:29:08.445
WHY ?
I HAVE MY OBSERVERS. AS I SAID.

486
00:29:08.513 --> 00:29:11.031
          AND IT'S POSSIBLE THAT
          THEY SAW LORD ARRYN...

487
00:29:11.099 --> 00:29:15.385
VISIT THIS ARMORER SEVERAL TIMES
IN THE WEEKS BEFORE HIS DEATH.

488
00:29:16.788 --> 00:29:19.539
LORD BAELISH.
PERHAPS I WAS WRONG
TO DISTRUST YOU.

489
00:29:19.608 --> 00:29:21.708
             DISTRUSTING ME WAS
             THE WISEST THING...

490
00:29:21.777 --> 00:29:24.545
         YOU'VE DONE SINCE YOU
         CLIMBED OFF YOUR HORSE.

491
00:29:31.286 --> 00:29:33.553
         (Hammering)
        ...22. 23...

492
00:29:33.622 --> 00:29:35.488
           24. 25...

493
00:29:35.557 --> 00:29:37.324
           26. 27...

494
00:29:37.392 --> 00:29:39.559
           28. 29--
          SER HUGH ?

495
00:29:39.628 --> 00:29:41.628
         30. 31. 32...

496
00:29:41.697 --> 00:29:43.913
                      SER HUGH !
AS YOU CAN SEE. I'M BUSY.

497
00:29:43.982 --> 00:29:46.933
           I'M HERE ON BEHALF OF
           LORD EDDARD STARK...

498
00:29:47.002 --> 00:29:49.218
           THE HAND OF THE KING.

499
00:29:49.287 --> 00:29:50.654
                 I'M THE CAPTAIN
                 OF HIS GUARD.

500
00:29:50.722 --> 00:29:52.823
I'M SORRY. I DIDN'T
CATCH YOUR NAME. SER...

501
00:29:52.891 --> 00:29:55.391
               NO "SER."
               I'M NOT A KNIGHT.

502
00:29:55.461 --> 00:29:58.695
I SEE. WELL. IT JUST
SO HAPPENS THAT I AM.

503
00:30:01.583 --> 00:30:03.617
      (Continues counting)

504
00:30:03.685 --> 00:30:06.920
  Jory: HE SAID HE'D BE GLAD
  TO TALK TO THE HAND HIMSELF.

505
00:30:06.988 --> 00:30:08.288
    HE'S A KNIGHT. YOU SEE.

506
00:30:08.357 --> 00:30:10.207
                   AH. A KNIGHT.

507
00:30:10.275 --> 00:30:14.127
        THEY STRUT AROUND
        LIKE ROOSTERS DOWN HERE.

508
00:30:14.195 --> 00:30:16.797
EVEN THE ONES WHO'VE NEVER
SEEN AN ARROW COMING THEIR WAY.

509
00:30:16.865 --> 00:30:18.665
YOU SHOULDN'T BE
OUT HERE. MY LORD.

510
00:30:18.734 --> 00:30:20.800
THERE'S NO TELLING
WHO HAS EYES WHERE.

511
00:30:20.869 --> 00:30:22.619
                  LET THEM LOOK.

512
00:30:24.205 --> 00:30:27.574
THE FORMER HAND DID CALL ON ME.
MY LORD. SEVERAL TIMES.

513
00:30:27.643 --> 00:30:30.744
I REGRET TO SAY
HE DID NOT HONOR ME
WITH HIS PATRONAGE.

514
00:30:30.813 --> 00:30:33.213
               WHAT DID
               LORD ARRYN WANT ?

515
00:30:33.281 --> 00:30:35.132
HE ALWAYS CAME
TO SEE THE BOY.

516
00:30:35.200 --> 00:30:37.050
                 I'D LIKE TO SEE
                 HIM AS WELL.

517
00:30:37.119 --> 00:30:39.452
AS YOU WISH. MY LORD.

518
00:30:39.521 --> 00:30:40.686
            GENDRY !

519
00:30:45.177 --> 00:30:46.609
         HERE HE IS.

520
00:30:46.678 --> 00:30:50.530
      STRONG FOR HIS AGE.
      HE WORKS HARD.

521
00:30:50.599 --> 00:30:53.016
     SHOW THE HAND THE
     HELMET YOU MADE. LAD.

522
00:31:06.498 --> 00:31:09.199
              THIS IS FINE WORK.
IT'S NOT FOR SALE.

523
00:31:09.268 --> 00:31:11.201
 BOY. THIS IS THE KING'S HAND !

524
00:31:11.270 --> 00:31:14.554
IF HIS LORDSHIP WANTS THE HELM--
I MADE IT FOR ME.

525
00:31:14.622 --> 00:31:17.006
       FORGIVE HIM. MY LORD.
     THERE'S NOTHING TO FORGIVE.

526
00:31:18.777 --> 00:31:22.379
         WHEN LORD ARRYN CAME TO
         VISIT YOU. WHAT WOULD
         YOU TALK ABOUT ?

527
00:31:22.447 --> 00:31:23.997
HE JUST ASKED ME
QUESTIONS IS ALL.
MY LORD.

528
00:31:24.065 --> 00:31:25.698
                    WHAT KIND OF
                    QUESTIONS ?

529
00:31:28.671 --> 00:31:31.538
ABOUT MY WORK
AT FIRST...

530
00:31:31.606 --> 00:31:34.708
IF I WAS BEING TREATED WELL.
IF I LIKED IT HERE.

531
00:31:36.645 --> 00:31:39.412
BUT THEN HE STARTED
ASKING ME ABOUT MY MOTHER.

532
00:31:39.481 --> 00:31:40.580
                   YOUR MOTHER ?

533
00:31:40.649 --> 00:31:43.767
WHO SHE WAS.
WHAT SHE LOOKED LIKE.

534
00:31:43.835 --> 00:31:45.903
         WHAT DID YOU TELL HIM ?

535
00:31:46.939 --> 00:31:49.806
  SHE DIED WHEN I WAS LITTLE.

536
00:31:49.875 --> 00:31:52.109
      SHE HAD YELLOW HAIR.

537
00:31:52.177 --> 00:31:54.594
  SHE'D SING TO ME SOMETIMES.

538
00:31:58.350 --> 00:31:59.716
                     LOOK AT ME.

539
00:32:10.245 --> 00:32:11.360
                     GET BACK TO
                     WORK. LAD.

540
00:32:14.032 --> 00:32:15.365
           IF THE DAY EVER COMES
           WHEN THAT BOY...

541
00:32:15.434 --> 00:32:18.835
      WOULD RATHER WIELD A SWORD
      THAN FORGE ONE...

542
00:32:18.903 --> 00:32:21.287
             YOU SEND HIM TO ME.

543
00:32:21.356 --> 00:32:22.923
        (Hammer banging)

544
00:32:24.626 --> 00:32:25.892
FIND ANYTHING ?

545
00:32:27.896 --> 00:32:30.563
                   KING ROBERT'S
                   BASTARD SON.

546
00:32:30.632 --> 00:32:33.800
       (Robert laughing)

547
00:32:33.868 --> 00:32:35.635
     Woman: HE LIKES THAT.
       (Women laughing)

548
00:32:37.238 --> 00:32:40.740
      THIS IS FOR THE KING
      FROM LORD STARK.

549
00:32:40.809 --> 00:32:42.375
       (Robert laughs)
  SHOULD I LEAVE IT WITH--

550
00:32:42.444 --> 00:32:44.194
             SHHH.

551
00:32:44.263 --> 00:32:46.562
           LISTEN.
     (Laughter continues)

552
00:32:46.631 --> 00:32:49.199
DO YOU HEAR THEM ?

553
00:32:51.019 --> 00:32:53.203
    HOW MANY DO YOU THINK
    ARE IN THERE WITH HIM ?

554
00:32:53.271 --> 00:32:54.253
             HUH ?

555
00:32:55.491 --> 00:32:57.524
                         GUESS.
            THREE ?

556
00:32:57.593 --> 00:32:59.059
          (Laughter)
            FOUR.

557
00:33:01.046 --> 00:33:03.547
      HE LIKES TO DO THIS
      WHEN I'M ON DUTY--

558
00:33:03.615 --> 00:33:06.333
    HE MAKES ME LISTEN
    AS HE INSULTS MY SISTER.

559
00:33:07.852 --> 00:33:09.252
     (Laughter continues)

560
00:33:11.723 --> 00:33:13.523
FORGIVE ME. MY LORD--
  WHY DO I HAVE TO FORGIVE YOU ?

561
00:33:13.591 --> 00:33:15.675
     HAVE YOU WRONGED ME ?

562
00:33:16.978 --> 00:33:18.645
WE'VE MET BEFORE.
YOU KNOW.

563
00:33:18.714 --> 00:33:21.714
        HAVE WE ?
        STRANGE. I'VE FORGOTTEN.

564
00:33:21.783 --> 00:33:25.251
THE SIEGE OF PYKE.
WE FOUGHT SIDE BY SIDE
ONE AFTERNOON.

565
00:33:25.320 --> 00:33:27.320
              AH.

566
00:33:27.388 --> 00:33:29.039
THAT'S WHERE YOU GOT YOUR SCAR ?
AYE.

567
00:33:29.107 --> 00:33:30.490
              OH.

568
00:33:30.558 --> 00:33:32.726
ONE OF THE GREYJOYS
NEARLY TOOK MY EYE.

569
00:33:32.795 --> 00:33:35.312
         VICIOUS SONS OF WHORES.
THEY LIKE THEIR BLOODSHED.

570
00:33:35.381 --> 00:33:37.114
             THEY STOPPED LIKING
             IT AT THE END.

571
00:33:38.634 --> 00:33:41.601
       THAT WAS A PROPER BATTLE.
       D'YOU REMEMBER...

572
00:33:41.670 --> 00:33:44.487
THOROS OF MYR CHARGING
THROUGH THE BREACH ?

573
00:33:44.556 --> 00:33:45.955
        WITH HIS BURNING SWORD ?

574
00:33:46.024 --> 00:33:48.525
             I'LL REMEMBER THAT
             TILL THE DAY I DIE.

575
00:33:48.594 --> 00:33:51.978
I SAW THE YOUNGEST
OF THE GREYJOY LADS
AT WINTERFELL.

576
00:33:52.047 --> 00:33:54.431
         IT WAS LIKE SEEING A
         SHARK ON A MOUNTAINTOP.

577
00:33:54.499 --> 00:33:56.700
THEON ?
HE'S A GOOD LAD.

578
00:33:56.769 --> 00:33:57.917
                     I DOUBT IT.

579
00:33:57.986 --> 00:34:00.403
          (Laughter)
         (Door opens)

580
00:34:02.774 --> 00:34:05.191
   Robert: I'LL BET YOU SMELL
   OF BLACKBERRY JAM !

581
00:34:05.259 --> 00:34:07.326
        LET ME SMELL IT.
        COME HERE.

582
00:34:09.764 --> 00:34:12.798
  CAN I LEAVE THIS WITH YOU ?
  THE MESSAGE FROM LORD STARK.

583
00:34:12.867 --> 00:34:14.684
   I DON'T SERVE LORD STARK.

584
00:34:19.007 --> 00:34:21.024
      (Laughter continues)

585
00:34:38.577 --> 00:34:40.777
    WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN ?
          WATCH DUTY.

586
00:34:40.845 --> 00:34:43.162
WITH SAM.
            AH. PRINCE PORKCHOP.

587
00:34:43.231 --> 00:34:45.181
                   WHERE IS HE ?
       HE WASN'T HUNGRY.

588
00:34:45.250 --> 00:34:47.000
         IMPOSSIBLE !
          (Chuckles)

589
00:34:47.069 --> 00:34:48.184
         THAT'S ENOUGH.

590
00:34:55.510 --> 00:34:58.378
      SAM'S NO DIFFERENT
      FROM THE REST OF US.

591
00:34:58.447 --> 00:35:02.198
THERE WAS NO PLACE
FOR HIM IN THE WORLD.
SO HE'S COME HERE.

592
00:35:02.267 --> 00:35:04.668
 WE'RE NOT GOING TO HURT HIM
 IN THE TRAINING YARD ANYMORE.

593
00:35:04.736 --> 00:35:07.604
  NEVER AGAIN.
  NO MATTER WHAT THORNE SAYS.

594
00:35:07.673 --> 00:35:10.239
  HE'S OUR BROTHER NOW AND
  WE'RE GOING TO PROTECT HIM.

595
00:35:10.308 --> 00:35:11.975
     Rast: YOU ARE IN LOVE.
     LORD SNOW.

596
00:35:12.043 --> 00:35:13.209
           (Laughter)

597
00:35:15.080 --> 00:35:17.881
YOU GIRLS CAN DO
AS YOU PLEASE.

598
00:35:17.950 --> 00:35:21.251
BUT IF THORNE PUTS ME
UP AGAINST LADY PIGGY...

599
00:35:21.320 --> 00:35:22.868
I'M GONNA SLICE ME OFF
A SIDE OF BACON.

600
00:35:22.937 --> 00:35:24.087
           (Laughter)

601
00:35:28.677 --> 00:35:30.944
          (Snoring)

602
00:35:41.856 --> 00:35:43.423
          (Panting)
          (Growling)

603
00:35:45.944 --> 00:35:47.810
      NO ONE TOUCHES SAM.

604
00:35:48.730 --> 00:35:50.613
            (Snarls)

605
00:35:50.682 --> 00:35:52.248
      (Growling continues)

606
00:36:03.261 --> 00:36:05.928
   WHAT ARE YOU WAITING FOR ?

607
00:36:15.207 --> 00:36:16.388
          ATTACK HIM !

608
00:36:26.684 --> 00:36:28.284
       YOU--GET IN THERE.

609
00:36:33.408 --> 00:36:34.924
        (Softly) HIT ME.

610
00:36:36.428 --> 00:36:37.643
GO ON. HIT ME !

611
00:36:39.047 --> 00:36:40.563
            (Shouts)

612
00:36:40.632 --> 00:36:42.982
          I YIELD !
          (Laughter)

613
00:36:43.068 --> 00:36:45.285
         YIELD. YIELD !

614
00:36:45.354 --> 00:36:46.552
           I YIELD !

615
00:36:50.158 --> 00:36:52.025
YOU THINK THIS
IS FUNNY. DO YOU ?

616
00:36:56.331 --> 00:36:57.680
    WHEN YOU'RE OUT THERE...

617
00:36:57.749 --> 00:37:01.167
   BEYOND THE WALL.
   WITH THE SUN GOING DOWN...

618
00:37:01.235 --> 00:37:02.869
       DO YOU WANT A MAN
       AT YOUR BACK...

619
00:37:02.937 --> 00:37:04.670
      OR A SNIVELING BOY ?

620
00:37:12.798 --> 00:37:14.146
           (Sobbing)

621
00:37:19.771 --> 00:37:22.489
     YOU SEND THIS WHORE
     TO GIVE ME COMMANDS ?

622
00:37:22.557 --> 00:37:25.074
      I SHOULD HAVE SENT
      YOU BACK HER HEAD !

623
00:37:25.143 --> 00:37:27.444
     FORGIVE ME. KHALEESI.
     I DID AS YOU ASKED.

624
00:37:27.512 --> 00:37:28.995
                 HUSH NOW.
                 IT'S ALL RIGHT.

625
00:37:29.064 --> 00:37:31.748
    IRRI. TAKE HER AND LEAVE US.
                  YES. KHALEESI.

626
00:37:35.553 --> 00:37:36.585
           WHY DID YOU HIT HER ?

627
00:37:36.654 --> 00:37:38.321
HOW MANY TIMES DO I
HAVE TO TELL YOU ?

628
00:37:38.390 --> 00:37:39.956
YOU DO NOT COMMAND ME.

629
00:37:40.024 --> 00:37:42.058
        I WASN'T COMMANDING YOU.

630
00:37:42.127 --> 00:37:43.626
         I JUST WANTED TO INVITE
         YOU TO SUPPER.

631
00:37:43.694 --> 00:37:45.929
         WHAT'S THIS ?
                    IT'S A GIFT.

632
00:37:45.998 --> 00:37:48.814
          I HAD IT MADE FOR YOU.
     DOTHRAKI RAGS ?

633
00:37:48.884 --> 00:37:51.000
ARE YOU GOING TO DRESS ME NOW ?
                         PLEASE.

634
00:37:51.068 --> 00:37:53.519
THIS STINKS OF MANURE.
ALL OF IT !

635
00:37:53.588 --> 00:37:55.672
         (Gasps) STOP-- STOP IT.

636
00:37:55.740 --> 00:37:57.240
YOU WOULD TURN ME INTO ONE
OF THEM. WOULDN'T YOU ?

637
00:37:57.309 --> 00:37:59.008
NEXT YOU'LL WANT
TO BRAID MY HAIR.

638
00:37:59.076 --> 00:38:02.312
    YOU'VE NO RIGHT TO A BRAID.
    YOU'VE WON NO VICTORIES YET.

639
00:38:02.380 --> 00:38:05.415
YOU DO NOT
TALK BACK TO ME !

640
00:38:06.984 --> 00:38:09.135
  YOU ARE A HORSELORD'S SLUT.

641
00:38:09.204 --> 00:38:11.604
AND NOW YOU'VE WOKEN
THE DRAGON--

642
00:38:16.978 --> 00:38:20.363
               I AM A KHALEESI
               OF THE DOTHRAKI !

643
00:38:20.432 --> 00:38:22.631
               I AM THE WIFE OF
               THE GREAT KHAL...

644
00:38:22.700 --> 00:38:25.668
                 AND I CARRY HIS
                 SON INSIDE ME.

645
00:38:25.736 --> 00:38:29.372
           THE NEXT TIME YOU
           RAISE A HAND TO ME...

646
00:38:29.441 --> 00:38:33.359
           WILL BE THE LAST TIME
           YOU HAVE HANDS.

647
00:38:35.213 --> 00:38:37.413
       (Thunder rumbles.
       rain pattering)

648
00:38:40.519 --> 00:38:42.118
    I KNOW FOR A FACT THAT
    SOME OF THE OFFICERS...

649
00:38:42.186 --> 00:38:43.820
       GO TO THAT BROTHEL
       IN MOLE'S TOWN.

650
00:38:43.888 --> 00:38:46.489
I WOULDN'T DOUBT IT.

651
00:38:46.558 --> 00:38:48.691
           DON'T YOU THINK IT'S
           A LITTLE BIT UNFAIR ?

652
00:38:48.760 --> 00:38:51.194
         MAKING US TAKE OUR VOWS
         WHILE THEY SNEAK OFF...

653
00:38:51.262 --> 00:38:54.146
             FOR A LITTLE
             SALLY ON THE SIDE ?

654
00:38:54.215 --> 00:38:56.583
SALLY ON THE SIDE ?
          IT'S SILLY. ISN'T IT ?

655
00:38:56.651 --> 00:39:00.552
 WHAT. WE CAN'T DEFEND THE WALL
 UNLESS WE'RE CELIBATE ?

656
00:39:00.621 --> 00:39:01.854
                    IT'S ABSURD.

657
00:39:01.923 --> 00:39:04.357
I DIDN'T THINK YOU'D BE
SO UPSET ABOUT IT.

658
00:39:05.610 --> 00:39:07.510
                       WHY NOT ?

659
00:39:07.578 --> 00:39:09.996
               BECAUSE I'M FAT ?
             NO--

660
00:39:10.065 --> 00:39:13.166
           BUT I LIKE GIRLS JUST
           AS MUCH AS YOU DO.

661
00:39:14.302 --> 00:39:17.337
                THEY MIGHT NOT
                LIKE ME AS MUCH.

662
00:39:18.606 --> 00:39:21.391
                  I'VE NEVER--
                  BEEN WITH ONE.

663
00:39:23.261 --> 00:39:25.662
                 YOU'VE PROBABLY
                 HAD HUNDREDS.

664
00:39:25.730 --> 00:39:27.530
              NO.

665
00:39:29.201 --> 00:39:30.567
AS A MATTER OF FACT...

666
00:39:31.586 --> 00:39:32.785
I'M THE SAME AS YOU.

667
00:39:32.854 --> 00:39:34.754
         (Scoffs) YEAH.

668
00:39:34.823 --> 00:39:37.540
                I FIND THAT HARD
                TO BELIEVE.

669
00:39:37.608 --> 00:39:39.008
I CAME VERY CLOSE ONCE.

670
00:39:40.345 --> 00:39:43.079
I WAS ALONE IN A ROOM
WITH A NAKED GIRL. BUT--

671
00:39:43.147 --> 00:39:45.364
               YOU DIDN'T KNOW
               WHERE TO PUT IT ?

672
00:39:45.433 --> 00:39:47.366
I KNOW WHERE TO PUT IT.

673
00:39:48.286 --> 00:39:49.652
                      WAS SHE...

674
00:39:49.721 --> 00:39:51.220
                  OLD AND UGLY ?

675
00:39:53.091 --> 00:39:55.307
      YOUNG AND GORGEOUS.

676
00:39:56.377 --> 00:39:57.860
A WHORE NAMED ROS.

677
00:40:00.248 --> 00:40:01.347
               WHAT COLOR HAIR ?

678
00:40:02.317 --> 00:40:05.485
RED.
            OH. I LIKE RED HAIR.

679
00:40:06.187 --> 00:40:08.488
                   AND HER. UM--

680
00:40:08.556 --> 00:40:10.406
                           HER--

681
00:40:10.475 --> 00:40:12.442
YOU DON'T WANT TO KNOW.
               WHAT. THAT GOOD ?

682
00:40:12.510 --> 00:40:15.077
BETTER.
                         OH. NO.

683
00:40:16.080 --> 00:40:18.848
             SO...WHY EXACTLY...

684
00:40:18.916 --> 00:40:21.651
     DID YOU NOT MAKE LOVE
     TO ROS WITH THE PERFECT-- ?

685
00:40:23.388 --> 00:40:24.854
WHAT'S MY NAME ?

686
00:40:24.923 --> 00:40:26.355
                      JON SNOW ?

687
00:40:27.826 --> 00:40:31.060
AND WHY IS MY
SURNAME SNOW ?

688
00:40:31.128 --> 00:40:32.161
                      BECAUSE...

689
00:40:33.397 --> 00:40:35.381
                YOU'RE A BASTARD
                FROM THE NORTH.

690
00:40:37.485 --> 00:40:39.986
I NEVER MET MY MOTHER.

691
00:40:40.054 --> 00:40:43.122
MY FATHER WOULDN'T EVEN
TELL ME HER NAME.

692
00:40:43.190 --> 00:40:46.092
I DON'T KNOW IF SHE'S
LIVING OR DEAD.

693
00:40:47.461 --> 00:40:50.062
I DON'T KNOW IF SHE'S
A NOBLEWOMAN...

694
00:40:50.131 --> 00:40:52.231
OR A FISHERMAN'S WIFE...

695
00:40:53.368 --> 00:40:54.500
          OR A WHORE.

696
00:40:57.488 --> 00:40:58.654
SO I SAT THERE...

697
00:40:59.925 --> 00:41:02.458
IN THE BROTHEL AS ROS
TOOK OFF HER CLOTHES.

698
00:41:04.446 --> 00:41:07.580
     BUT I COULDN'T DO IT.

699
00:41:07.648 --> 00:41:09.815
      BECAUSE ALL I COULD
      THINK WAS...

700
00:41:09.884 --> 00:41:11.584
 WHAT IF I GOT HER PREGNANT...

701
00:41:12.454 --> 00:41:14.987
     AND SHE HAD A CHILD--

702
00:41:15.056 --> 00:41:18.191
  ANOTHER BASTARD NAMED SNOW ?

703
00:41:21.996 --> 00:41:24.747
      IT'S NOT A GOOD LIFE
      FOR A CHILD.

704
00:41:24.816 --> 00:41:26.549
                        AH. MMM.

705
00:41:29.888 --> 00:41:30.987
                           SO...

706
00:41:32.223 --> 00:41:33.872
               YOU DIDN'T KNOW
               WHERE TO PUT IT ?

707
00:41:36.677 --> 00:41:37.877
          (Laughter)

708
00:41:39.948 --> 00:41:41.381
ENJOYING YOURSELVES ?

709
00:41:44.101 --> 00:41:45.835
      YOU LOOK COLD. BOYS.

710
00:41:45.903 --> 00:41:47.403
         (Door creaks)

711
00:41:47.472 --> 00:41:48.938
IT IS A BIT NIPPY.

712
00:41:49.006 --> 00:41:51.874
A BIT NIPPY.
YEAH. BY THE FIRE...

713
00:41:51.943 --> 00:41:52.908
INDOORS.

714
00:41:54.045 --> 00:41:56.512
IT'S STILL THE SUMMER.

715
00:41:56.581 --> 00:41:58.881
DO YOU BOYS EVEN REMEMBER
THE LAST WINTER ?

716
00:42:00.518 --> 00:42:03.152
HOW LONG HAS IT BEEN NOW ?
WHAT. 10 YEARS ?

717
00:42:04.589 --> 00:42:06.139
          I REMEMBER.

718
00:42:06.207 --> 00:42:08.841
WAS IT UNCOMFORTABLE
AT WINTERFELL ?

719
00:42:08.909 --> 00:42:10.876
WERE THERE DAYS WHEN YOU
JUST COULDN'T GET WARM...

720
00:42:10.945 --> 00:42:14.230
NEVER MIND HOW MANY FIRES
YOUR SERVANTS BUILT ?

721
00:42:14.298 --> 00:42:16.833
           I BUILD MY OWN FIRES.
THAT'S ADMIRABLE.

722
00:42:18.402 --> 00:42:21.637
 I SPENT SIX MONTHS OUT THERE.
 BEYOND THE WALL...

723
00:42:21.706 --> 00:42:23.138
    DURING THE LAST WINTER.

724
00:42:25.160 --> 00:42:28.161
IT WAS SUPPOSED TO BE
A TWO-WEEK MISSION.

725
00:42:28.229 --> 00:42:31.414
WE HEARD A RUMOR
MANCE RAYDER WAS PLANNING
TO ATTACK EASTWATCH.

726
00:42:31.482 --> 00:42:34.583
SO WE WENT OUT TO LOOK
FOR SOME OF HIS MEN--

727
00:42:34.652 --> 00:42:37.136
CAPTURE THEM.
GATHER SOME KNOWLEDGE.

728
00:42:37.205 --> 00:42:40.957
THE WILDLINGS WHO FIGHT
FOR MANCE RAYDER
ARE HARD MEN.

729
00:42:41.025 --> 00:42:43.292
HARDER THAN YOU'LL EVER BE.

730
00:42:43.360 --> 00:42:45.761
THEY KNOW THEIR COUNTRY
BETTER THAN WE DO.

731
00:42:45.830 --> 00:42:49.198
THEY KNEW THERE WAS
A STORM COMING IN.

732
00:42:49.267 --> 00:42:53.202
SO THEY HID IN THEIR CAVES
AND WAITED FOR IT TO PASS.

733
00:42:54.272 --> 00:42:56.672
AND WE GOT CAUGHT
IN THE OPEN.

734
00:42:56.741 --> 00:42:58.507
WIND SO STRONG...

735
00:42:58.576 --> 00:43:01.143
IT YANKED 100-FOOT TREES
STRAIGHT FROM THE GROUND...

736
00:43:01.212 --> 00:43:03.662
 ROOTS AND ALL.
 IF YOU TOOK YOUR GLOVES OFF...

737
00:43:03.731 --> 00:43:05.698
TO FIND YOUR COCK
TO HAVE A PISS...

738
00:43:05.766 --> 00:43:08.667
YOU LOST A FINGER
TO THE FROST.

739
00:43:08.736 --> 00:43:11.337
AND ALL IN DARKNESS.

740
00:43:13.874 --> 00:43:16.442
YOU DON'T KNOW COLD.

741
00:43:16.511 --> 00:43:17.843
NEITHER OF YOU DO.

742
00:43:20.865 --> 00:43:22.431
THE HORSES DIED FIRST.

743
00:43:25.470 --> 00:43:29.204
WE DIDN'T HAVE
ENOUGH TO FEED THEM.
TO KEEP THEM WARM.

744
00:43:30.575 --> 00:43:33.910
EATING THE HORSES
WAS EASY.

745
00:43:35.179 --> 00:43:38.948
BUT LATER WHEN WE
STARTED TO FALL--

746
00:43:39.985 --> 00:43:41.334
THAT WASN'T EASY.

747
00:43:43.171 --> 00:43:46.505
WE SHOULD HAVE HAD
A COUPLE OF BOYS LIKE YOU
ALONG. SHOULDN'T WE ?

748
00:43:50.412 --> 00:43:54.179
            (Gasps)
    SOFT. FAT BOYS LIKE YOU.

749
00:43:54.248 --> 00:43:56.516
             WE'D HAVE LASTED A
             FORTNIGHT ON YOU...

750
00:43:56.584 --> 00:43:58.851
             AND STILL HAD BONES
             LEFT OVER FOR SOUP.

751
00:44:02.239 --> 00:44:04.874
                 SOON WE'LL HAVE
                 NEW RECRUITS...

752
00:44:04.943 --> 00:44:08.344
AND YOU LOT WILL BE PASSED ALONG
TO THE LORD COMMANDER...

753
00:44:08.412 --> 00:44:10.412
FOR ASSIGNMENT...

754
00:44:10.482 --> 00:44:14.833
AND THEY WILL CALL YOU
MEN OF THE NIGHT'S WATCH...

755
00:44:14.902 --> 00:44:18.170
BUT YOU'D BE FOOLS
TO BELIEVE IT.

756
00:44:18.239 --> 00:44:20.139
YOU'RE BOYS STILL.

757
00:44:20.207 --> 00:44:23.008
AND COME THE WINTER
YOU WILL DIE...

758
00:44:25.463 --> 00:44:27.096
LIKE FLIES.

759
00:44:33.754 --> 00:44:34.853
           I HIT HIM.

760
00:44:36.190 --> 00:44:37.356
       I HIT THE DRAGON.

761
00:44:37.425 --> 00:44:39.826
            YOUR BROTHER RHAEGAR
            WAS THE LAST DRAGON.

762
00:44:39.894 --> 00:44:42.695
          VISERYS IS LESS THAN
          THE SHADOW OF A SNAKE.

763
00:44:42.764 --> 00:44:44.497
HE IS STILL
THE TRUE KING.

764
00:44:44.565 --> 00:44:46.932
                 THE TRUTH NOW--

765
00:44:47.001 --> 00:44:49.935
            DO YOU WANT TO SEE
            YOUR BROTHER SITTING
            ON THE IRON THRONE ?

766
00:44:51.005 --> 00:44:53.239
NO.

767
00:44:53.307 --> 00:44:55.791
BUT THE COMMON PEOPLE
ARE WAITING FOR HIM.

768
00:44:55.860 --> 00:44:59.929
ILLYRIO SAID THEY ARE
SEWING DRAGON BANNERS
AND PRAYING FOR HIS RETURN.

769
00:44:59.997 --> 00:45:04.834
       THE COMMON PEOPLE
       PRAY FOR RAIN. HEALTH AND
       A SUMMER THAT NEVER ENDS.

770
00:45:04.903 --> 00:45:08.187
      THEY DON'T CARE WHAT GAMES
      THE HIGH LORDS PLAY.

771
00:45:08.255 --> 00:45:11.407
WHAT DO YOU PRAY FOR.
SER JORAH ?

772
00:45:14.645 --> 00:45:15.844
                           HOME.

773
00:45:17.815 --> 00:45:20.650
I PRAY FOR HOME TOO.

774
00:45:23.487 --> 00:45:27.873
MY BROTHER
WILL NEVER TAKE BACK
THE SEVEN KINGDOMS.

775
00:45:27.942 --> 00:45:32.077
HE COULDN'T LEAD AN ARMY.
EVEN IF MY HUSBAND
GAVE HIM ONE.

776
00:45:34.516 --> 00:45:36.249
HE'LL NEVER TAKE US HOME.

777
00:45:39.003 --> 00:45:41.236
       (Crowd chattering)

778
00:45:56.854 --> 00:45:58.103
       LOVER'S QUARREL ?

779
00:45:59.240 --> 00:46:00.539
      I'M SORRY. DO I-- ?

780
00:46:00.607 --> 00:46:03.759
   SANSA DEAR. THIS IS
   LORD BAELISH. HE'S KNOWN--

781
00:46:03.828 --> 00:46:06.278
AN OLD FRIEND
OF THE FAMILY.

782
00:46:06.347 --> 00:46:08.547
I'VE KNOWN YOUR MOTHER
A LONG. LONG TIME.

783
00:46:08.615 --> 00:46:10.099
            WHY DO THEY CALL YOU
            LITTLEFINGER ?

784
00:46:10.168 --> 00:46:12.218
            ARYA !
                 DON'T BE RUDE !

785
00:46:12.287 --> 00:46:13.702
NO. IT'S QUITE
ALL RIGHT.

786
00:46:14.739 --> 00:46:18.007
WHEN I WAS A CHILD
I WAS VERY SMALL..

787
00:46:18.075 --> 00:46:20.176
AND I COME FROM
A LITTLE SPIT OF LAND
CALLED THE FINGERS...

788
00:46:20.245 --> 00:46:22.345
SO YOU SEE...

789
00:46:22.413 --> 00:46:24.263
IT'S AN EXCEEDINGLY
CLEVER NICKNAME.

790
00:46:24.332 --> 00:46:27.332
I'VE BEEN SITTING
HERE FOR DAYS !

791
00:46:27.402 --> 00:46:29.201
START THE
DAMN JOUST...

792
00:46:29.270 --> 00:46:31.887
BEFORE I
PISS MYSELF !

793
00:46:32.857 --> 00:46:33.972
           (Cheering)

794
00:46:38.930 --> 00:46:41.964
      GODS. WHO IS THAT ?

795
00:46:42.033 --> 00:46:43.499
      Baelish:
      SER GREGOR CLEGANE.

796
00:46:43.567 --> 00:46:45.735
  THEY CALL HIM THE MOUNTAIN.

797
00:46:48.122 --> 00:46:50.806
   THE HOUND'S OLDER BROTHER.

798
00:46:50.875 --> 00:46:51.957
       AND HIS OPPONENT ?

799
00:46:52.025 --> 00:46:54.226
     Baelish:
     SER HUGH OF THE VALE.

800
00:46:54.295 --> 00:46:56.128
   HE WAS JON ARRYN'S SQUIRE.

801
00:46:56.197 --> 00:46:57.997
    LOOK HOW FAR HE'S COME.

802
00:46:58.066 --> 00:47:00.232
      YES. YES. ENOUGH
      OF THE BLOODY POMP.

803
00:47:00.301 --> 00:47:01.517
         HAVE AT HIM !

804
00:47:07.007 --> 00:47:08.223
       (Plays fanfare)

805
00:47:10.378 --> 00:47:11.577
         (Horse neighs)

806
00:47:42.543 --> 00:47:43.542
           (Screams)

807
00:47:44.712 --> 00:47:45.844
         (Crowd gasps)

808
00:47:47.348 --> 00:47:48.514
           (Gurgling)

809
00:48:22.199 --> 00:48:23.799
NOT WHAT YOU
WERE EXPECTING ?

810
00:48:27.771 --> 00:48:32.708
HAS ANYONE EVER TOLD YOU
THE STORY OF THE MOUNTAIN
AND THE HOUND ?

811
00:48:32.777 --> 00:48:36.061
              LOVELY LITTLE TALE
              OF BROTHERLY LOVE.

812
00:48:37.148 --> 00:48:39.982
THE HOUND WAS
JUST A PUP...

813
00:48:40.051 --> 00:48:42.251
SIX YEARS OLD. MAYBE.

814
00:48:42.320 --> 00:48:44.320
GREGOR A FEW YEARS OLDER--

815
00:48:44.388 --> 00:48:48.123
ALREADY A BIG LAD.
ALREADY GETTING A BIT
OF A REPUTATION.

816
00:48:48.192 --> 00:48:49.842
SOME LUCKY BOYS...

817
00:48:49.911 --> 00:48:54.580
JUST BORN WITH A
TALENT FOR VIOLENCE.

818
00:48:54.649 --> 00:48:57.750
    ONE EVENING GREGOR FOUND
    HIS LITTLE BROTHER...

819
00:48:57.818 --> 00:49:00.318
       PLAYING WITH A TOY
       BY THE FIRE--

820
00:49:00.387 --> 00:49:02.588
        GREGOR'S TOY...

821
00:49:02.656 --> 00:49:04.389
        A WOODEN KNIGHT.

822
00:49:05.659 --> 00:49:07.693
  GREGOR NEVER SAID A WORD...

823
00:49:07.762 --> 00:49:10.446
  HE JUST GRABBED HIS BROTHER
  BY THE SCRUFF OF HIS NECK...

824
00:49:10.515 --> 00:49:14.033
    AND SHOVED HIS FACE
    INTO THE BURNING COALS.

825
00:49:14.101 --> 00:49:15.801
       HELD HIM THERE...

826
00:49:15.870 --> 00:49:17.770
   WHILE THE BOY SCREAMED...

827
00:49:17.838 --> 00:49:19.438
     WHILE HIS FACE MELTED.

828
00:49:24.612 --> 00:49:28.113
THERE AREN'T VERY MANY PEOPLE
WHO KNOW THAT STORY.

829
00:49:28.182 --> 00:49:30.082
            I WON'T TELL ANYONE.
            I PROMISE.

830
00:49:30.150 --> 00:49:31.851
NO. PLEASE DON'T.

831
00:49:31.919 --> 00:49:35.187
IF THE HOUND SO MUCH AS
HEARD YOU MENTION IT...

832
00:49:35.256 --> 00:49:37.390
I'M AFRAID ALL THE KNIGHTS
IN KING'S LANDING...

833
00:49:37.458 --> 00:49:39.258
WOULD NOT BE ABLE
TO SAVE YOU.

834
00:49:50.103 --> 00:49:51.269
          (Knocking)

835
00:49:52.372 --> 00:49:55.223
      MY LORD.
      HER GRACE THE QUEEN.

836
00:49:58.696 --> 00:50:01.113
YOUR GRACE.
YOU'RE MISSING YOUR TOURNAMENT.

837
00:50:01.181 --> 00:50:03.749
     PUTTING MY NAME ON IT
     DOESN'T MAKE IT MINE.

838
00:50:06.004 --> 00:50:09.654
          I THOUGHT WE MIGHT PUT
          WHAT HAPPENED ON THE
          KINGSROAD BEHIND US--

839
00:50:09.723 --> 00:50:13.358
                THE UGLINESS
                WITH THE WOLVES.

840
00:50:13.427 --> 00:50:17.295
         AND FORCING YOU TO KILL
         THE BEAST WAS EXTREME.

841
00:50:17.364 --> 00:50:22.167
        THOUGH SOMETIMES WE
        GO TO EXTREMES WHERE OUR
        CHILDREN ARE CONCERNED.

842
00:50:22.236 --> 00:50:23.302
                  HOW IS SANSA ?

843
00:50:24.806 --> 00:50:26.138
       SHE LIKES IT HERE.

844
00:50:26.207 --> 00:50:27.606
        SHE'S THE ONLY
        STARK WHO DOES.

845
00:50:27.675 --> 00:50:30.242
            FAVORS HER MOTHER...

846
00:50:30.311 --> 00:50:31.861
                 NOT MUCH OF THE
                 NORTH IN HER.

847
00:50:31.929 --> 00:50:35.664
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE ?
    I MIGHT ASK THE SAME OF YOU.

848
00:50:35.733 --> 00:50:37.999
            WHAT IS IT YOU
            HOPE TO ACCOMPLISH ?

849
00:50:38.069 --> 00:50:40.719
THE KING CALLED ON ME TO
SERVE HIM AND THE REALM...

850
00:50:40.788 --> 00:50:43.305
AND THAT'S WHAT I'LL DO
UNTIL HE TELLS ME OTHERWISE.

851
00:50:43.374 --> 00:50:46.075
           YOU CAN'T CHANGE HIM.
           YOU CAN'T HELP HIM.

852
00:50:46.143 --> 00:50:48.744
             HE'LL DO WHAT HE
             WANTS. WHICH IS
             ALL HE'S EVER DONE.

853
00:50:48.812 --> 00:50:51.613
          YOU'LL TRY YOUR BEST
          TO PICK UP THE PIECES.

854
00:50:51.682 --> 00:50:54.250
IF THAT'S MY JOB.
THEN SO BE IT.

855
00:50:56.036 --> 00:50:58.303
          YOU'RE JUST A SOLDIER.
          AREN'T YOU ?

856
00:50:58.372 --> 00:51:00.706
            YOU TAKE YOUR ORDERS
            AND YOU CARRY ON.

857
00:51:02.109 --> 00:51:04.459
                    I SUPPOSE IT
                    MAKES SENSE.

858
00:51:04.528 --> 00:51:07.395
         YOUR OLDER BROTHER WAS
         TRAINED TO LEAD AND YOU
         WERE TRAINED TO FOLLOW.

859
00:51:07.464 --> 00:51:10.182
I WAS ALSO TRAINED TO KILL
MY ENEMIES. YOUR GRACE.

860
00:51:14.238 --> 00:51:15.537
           AS WAS I.

861
00:51:20.945 --> 00:51:24.246
      (Door opens. closes)

862
00:51:32.106 --> 00:51:33.105
         (Dog barking)

863
00:51:34.425 --> 00:51:37.042
    SEVEN BLESSINGS TO YOU.
    GOODFOLK !

864
00:51:37.110 --> 00:51:38.243
          AND TO YOU.

865
00:51:38.312 --> 00:51:40.379
BOY ! BREAD. MEAT
AND BEER. QUICKLY.

866
00:51:40.447 --> 00:51:43.348
                  AH. GOOD IDEA.
                  GRANDFATHER.
                  I'M STARVING.

867
00:51:43.417 --> 00:51:44.850
A SONG WHILE
WE WAIT OR-- ?

868
00:51:44.919 --> 00:51:47.018
      I'D RATHER THROW
      MYSELF DOWN A WELL.

869
00:51:47.087 --> 00:51:50.239
    NOW. NOW. GRANDFATHER.
    THIS MAY BE YOUR LAST CHANCE
    IF YOU'RE HEADING NORTH.

870
00:51:50.307 --> 00:51:54.309
THE ONLY MUSIC THE NORTHERNERS
KNOW IS THE HOWLING OF WOLVES !
(Laughs)

871
00:51:54.378 --> 00:51:57.046
         (Door opens)
GODS.

872
00:51:57.114 --> 00:52:00.032
             I'M SORRY. MY LORD.
             WE'RE FULL UP.
             EVERY ROOM.

873
00:52:00.101 --> 00:52:01.800
      Tyrion: MY MEN CAN
      SLEEP IN THE STABLE.

874
00:52:01.868 --> 00:52:04.937
     AS FOR MYSELF. I DON'T
     REQUIRE A LARGE ROOM.

875
00:52:05.005 --> 00:52:07.806
                TRULY. MY LORD.
                WE HAVE NOTHING.

876
00:52:07.875 --> 00:52:10.008
IS THERE NOTHING
I CAN DO...

877
00:52:10.077 --> 00:52:12.394
        (Coin clanks)
...TO REMEDY THIS ?

878
00:52:12.463 --> 00:52:14.396
           YOU CAN HAVE MY ROOM.

879
00:52:14.465 --> 00:52:15.764
   NOW THERE'S A CLEVER MAN.

880
00:52:17.368 --> 00:52:20.452
 YOU CAN MANAGE FOOD. I TRUST ?
 YOREN. DINE WITH ME.

881
00:52:20.521 --> 00:52:22.371
         AYE. MY LORD.
MY LORD OF LANNISTER !

882
00:52:22.440 --> 00:52:24.906
MIGHT I ENTERTAIN YOU
WHILE YOU EAT ?

883
00:52:24.975 --> 00:52:27.759
I CAN SING OF
YOUR FATHER'S VICTORY
AT KING'S LANDING !

884
00:52:27.828 --> 00:52:31.497
          NOTHING WOULD MORE
          LIKELY RUIN MY SUPPER.

885
00:52:31.565 --> 00:52:33.866
                    LADY STARK !

886
00:52:33.934 --> 00:52:35.584
              WHAT AN UNEXPECTED
              PLEASURE.

887
00:52:37.037 --> 00:52:39.271
       I WAS SORRY TO HAVE
       MISSED YOU AT WINTERFELL.

888
00:52:39.340 --> 00:52:41.056
          LADY STARK !

889
00:52:49.183 --> 00:52:51.149
I WAS STILL
CATELYN TULLY...

890
00:52:51.218 --> 00:52:53.218
THE LAST TIME
I STAYED HERE.

891
00:52:56.290 --> 00:52:57.690
YOU. SER...

892
00:52:59.460 --> 00:53:03.712
IS THAT THE BLACK BAT
OF HARRENHAL I SEE
EMBROIDERED ON YOUR COAT ?

893
00:53:03.780 --> 00:53:05.214
        IT IS. MY LADY.

894
00:53:05.282 --> 00:53:08.083
  AND IS LADY WHENT
  A TRUE AND HONEST FRIEND...

895
00:53:08.152 --> 00:53:12.254
TO MY FATHER.
LORD HOSTER TULLY OF RIVERRUN ?

896
00:53:12.322 --> 00:53:13.288
            SHE IS.

897
00:53:15.976 --> 00:53:19.278
  THE RED STALLION WAS ALWAYS
  A WELCOME SIGHT AT RIVERRUN.

898
00:53:19.347 --> 00:53:21.513
        MY FATHER COUNTS
        JONAS BRACKEN...

899
00:53:21.582 --> 00:53:24.699
AMONGST HIS OLDEST AND
MOST LOYAL BANNERMEN.

900
00:53:24.768 --> 00:53:27.670
      OUR LORD IS HONORED
      BY HIS TRUST.

901
00:53:27.738 --> 00:53:28.904
     I ENVY YOUR FATHER...

902
00:53:28.972 --> 00:53:31.574
     ALL HIS FINE FRIENDS.
     LADY STARK. BUT...

903
00:53:31.642 --> 00:53:33.975
      I DON'T QUITE SEE
      THE PURPOSE OF THIS.

904
00:53:35.663 --> 00:53:38.781
  I KNOW YOUR SIGIL AS WELL--

905
00:53:38.849 --> 00:53:41.583
    THE TWIN TOWERS OF FREY.

906
00:53:41.652 --> 00:53:43.285
   HOW FARES YOUR LORD. SER ?

907
00:53:44.555 --> 00:53:46.305
 LORD WALDER IS WELL. MY LADY.

908
00:53:46.373 --> 00:53:50.059
 HE HAS ASKED YOUR FATHER
 FOR THE HONOR OF HIS PRESENCE
 ON HIS 90th NAMEDAY.

909
00:53:50.127 --> 00:53:52.110
HE PLANS TO TAKE ANOTHER WIFE.
             HA !

910
00:53:59.403 --> 00:54:01.403
          THIS MAN...

911
00:54:01.472 --> 00:54:03.855
       CAME INTO MY HOUSE
       AS A GUEST...

912
00:54:03.924 --> 00:54:07.759
             AND THERE CONSPIRED
             TO MURDER MY SON...

913
00:54:08.879 --> 00:54:10.211
          A BOY OF 10.

914
00:54:13.099 --> 00:54:16.802
IN THE NAME OF KING ROBERT
AND THE GOOD LORDS YOU SERVE...

915
00:54:16.870 --> 00:54:19.905
        I CALL UPON YOU
        TO SEIZE HIM...

916
00:54:19.974 --> 00:54:22.641
     AND HELP ME RETURN HIM
     TO WINTERFELL...

917
00:54:22.710 --> 00:54:25.360
  TO AWAIT THE KING'S JUSTICE.
